# wy-frontend Conventions

Stack: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, axios.

- Organize features under `src/app/(feature)/...` (e.g., `(events)`, `(profile)`).
- Use shared UI from `src/components/ui/*` and icons/helpers in `src/components/icons/*`.
- Align TypeScript types with backend Pydantic schemas; colocate `types.ts` near the feature.
- Prefer small, composable edits; follow existing patterns and directories.

Key paths:
- Routes root: `src/app/`
- HTTP client: [axiosInstance.ts](mdc:wy-frontend/src/lib/axiosInstance.ts)
- Shared UI: `src/components/ui/*`
- Contexts: `src/context/*`
- Helpers: `src/app/retreats/helpers.ts`

See also: [guidelines.mdc](mdc:wy-frontend/.cursor/rules/guidelines.mdc)

Local dev:
- Install: `yarn install`
- Run: `yarn dev` (ensure `.env.local` is configured)

For deeper orientation, read [README.md](mdc:wy-frontend/README.md) and project `ARCHITECTURE.md`.
